{"title":"西财猫剧场｜让猫咪躲进你的屏幕里","uid":"6590629b85d0572659e990e6ca087325","slug":"推文15","date":"2021-11-19T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T17:00:13.523Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文15.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003804509.png","content":"<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003804509.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003804509\"></p>\n<p>寻一个橘子辉煌的天</p>\n<p>把透明糖罐里的细碎阳光</p>\n<p>一股脑全撒在这些演员上</p>\n<p>校园里的猫剧场</p>\n<p>就会慢慢沸腾起来</p>\n<p>每一只猫咪</p>\n<p>都已然或者终将</p>\n<p>成为我们的国王</p>\n<p>披上战袍</p>\n<p>巡视在整个校园</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003816800.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003816800\">▲李荣浩</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003821850.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003821850\"></p>\n<p>▲灰老板（毕业）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003841229.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003841229\"></p>\n<p> ▲卷卷</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003849707.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003849707\"></p>\n<p>▲大海参</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003900744.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003900744\"></p>\n<p> ▲小笨蛋</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003909674.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003909674\"></p>\n<p>▲壮壮</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003916541.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003916541\"></p>\n<p> ▲美团</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003924834.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003924834\"></p>\n<p> ▲呆呆</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003931780.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003931780\"></p>\n<p>▲绿宝石<img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003939621.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003939621\"></p>\n<p>▲嗷呜</p>\n<p><strong>光华剧场将军名录</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004001043.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004001043\"></p>\n<p>▲小橘</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004008645.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004008645\"></p>\n<p>▲小白</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004014873.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004014873\"></p>\n<p> ▲棕橘</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004029946.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004029946\"></p>\n<p>▲家属区橘白</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004037592.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004037592\"></p>\n<p>▲奶牛</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004046261.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004046261\"></p>\n<p>▲绿眼大橘</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004059263.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004059263\"></p>\n<p>▲大橘白</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004116739.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004116739\"></p>\n<p>▲棕橘</p>\n<p>捧着半开的栗子香</p>\n<p>伴着随性的喵喵乐谱</p>\n<p>前戏已经开场</p>\n<p>剧场开幕</p>\n<p>不知是这深秋的桂花糕，</p>\n<p>还是糖炒栗子的香气，</p>\n<p>勾来了这小馋猫。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004132654.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004132654\"></p>\n<p> ▲小橘</p>\n<p>虽然也是在某个阳光温暖了我每一根胡须的午后，妈妈告诉说不要乱碰别人的东西。</p>\n<p>但我知道这是可爱的人类为我准备的礼物，他们期望我当场拆开。我也有记得说谢谢。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004142497.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004142497\"></p>\n<p> ▲小乖</p>\n<p>有时候，</p>\n<p>相遇也变成一个难忘的回忆。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004150469.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004150469\"></p>\n<p> ▲奶茶与豆包</p>\n<p>和往常一样，和太阳说过再见，妈妈就已经开始打盹。</p>\n<p>可那一天，我的悄悄话还没说出口，太阳也看出我的迟疑，就用尾巴在墙上留言一字一画，背着妈妈我又和TA说了好久好久。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004206036.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004206036\"></p>\n<p> ▲小乖与通博楼大橘</p>\n<p>距离10公分外的客人</p>\n<p>一只热情的猫咪</p>\n<p>要拿出51分贝的音量</p>\n<p>来招揽你注意</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004216809.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004216809\"></p>\n<p>▲豆包</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004223696.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004223696\"></p>\n<p>   ▲肥宅</p>\n<p>精灵失落的小花球</p>\n<p>掉落人间</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004237184.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004237184\"></p>\n<p>▲脏脏</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004245958.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004245958\"></p>\n<p> ▲壮壮</p>\n<p>东门工地旁</p>\n<p>是与你相伴的冬天</p>\n<p>今年初雪落下时</p>\n<p>会有猫咪躲进你的屏幕里</p>\n<p>留下一串小梅花吗？</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004254960.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004254960\"></p>\n<p>▲小异瞳与豆包</p>\n<p>写在最后</p>\n<p>每一只猫猫都是财大人的天使</p>\n<p>束上红妆每一场布景后</p>\n<p>都是经常呈现</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004307040.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004307040\"></p>\n<p>那些我们熟悉的或是不熟悉的毛绒身影</p>\n<p>曾经在路沿上眯眼晒太阳</p>\n<p>曾经在草丛间互扑玩闹</p>\n<p>曾经特立独行</p>\n<p>曾经平凡普通</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004314160.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004314160\"></p>\n<p>或许在西财生活的间隙中</p>\n<p>你也曾见过这些美丽的天使踏足人间</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004324189.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004324189\"></p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>感谢</summary>\n<p>摄影｜李俊 徐小茹 易钰垒</p>\n<p>李宜霏 刘雨童 罗雯曦 徐皓辰</p>\n<p>罗昌嘉 韦镕坡 张液 杨康 赵书铮</p>\n<p>文｜宁先会 李宜霏</p>\n<p>排版｜李宜霏 刘雨童</p>\n\n</details>\n","text":" 寻一个橘子辉煌的天 把透明糖罐里的细碎阳光 一股脑全撒在这些演员上 校园里的猫剧场 就会慢慢沸腾起来 每一只猫咪 都已然或者终将 成为我们的国王 披上战袍 巡视在整个校园 ▲李荣浩 ▲灰老板（毕业） ▲卷卷 ▲大海参 ▲小笨蛋 ▲壮壮 ▲美团 ▲呆呆 ▲绿宝石 ▲嗷呜 光华剧场...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":806,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财猫剧场","slug":"西财猫剧场","count":1,"path":"api/categories/西财猫剧场.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"猫","slug":"猫","count":1,"path":"api/tags/猫.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303234741533.png"},"mail":{"icon":"/img/mail.png","link":"mailto:271215314@qq.com"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"西财摄记 | Round and round","uid":"1fc4783e0d5bd21de1c0f61ddfb36851","slug":"推文16","date":"2021-11-22T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T16:49:19.924Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文16.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004525721.png","text":"“It’s beautiful life, Beautiful day.” 再一次迎来属于你我的季节 你还会记得吗 听说人会经历四次人生 可能的话，希望这是第一生 那样的话 第二生，第三生，还有最后一生 都能与你相遇 一召唤就会有回应的声音 在同一时间看过同一事物的回忆 彼此首次...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":631,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":9,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"秋","slug":"秋","count":5,"path":"api/tags/秋.json"}],"author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303234741533.png"},"